                <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
                    <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="LAP_WEAP_Talon_Horus"]/label</xpath>
                    <value>
                        <label>the Warmaster's Talon</label>
                    </value>
                </li>

                <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
                    <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="LAP_WEAP_Talon_Horus"]/description</xpath>
                    <value>
                        <description>A unique lightning claw which incorporates a baroquely styled twin-bolter, the Warmaster's Talon has long been Horus' favoured weapon. Some apocryphal sources claim it is an antediluvian relic that was found deep on the planet Clthon, and was a product of Mankind's Dark Age of Technology.\n\nHorus was the Primarch of the Luna Wolves Legion and greatest of his superhuman kind. A tactical genius and charismatic battle leader, Horus proved himself over the course of the Great Crusade as a warlord second only to the Emperor who he served and called father. So it was that when the Emperor stood apart from the burden of command of the Great Crusade, it was Horus that He named Warmaster to act in His stead.</description>
                    </value>
                </li>

